Preheat oven to 350 degrees F (180 degrees C). In a mixing bowl, cream the shortening and peanut butter. Add the brown sugar, eggs, and vanilla; mix well. Combine oats, flour, baking soda, and salt; add to the creamed mixture and mix well. Drop by the rounded teaspoonfuls onto ungreased baking sheet. Flatten with fork. Bake for 12 minutes or until done.